equation: (ventricularInteraction_flat.Vlv - ventricularInteraction_flat.Vsept) * ventricularInteraction_flat.A * exp((-ventricularInteraction_flat.B) * (ventricularInteraction_flat.tm - ventricularInteraction_flat.CC) ^ 2.0) * ventricularInteraction_flat.Eslv + (1.0 - ventricularInteraction_flat.A * exp((-ventricularInteraction_flat.B) * (ventricularInteraction_flat.tm - ventricularInteraction_flat.CC) ^ 2.0)) * ventricularInteraction_flat.Pi0lv * (-1.0 + exp(ventricularInteraction_flat.lambdalv * (ventricularInteraction_flat.Vlv - ventricularInteraction_flat.Vsept))) + ventricularInteraction_flat.Pperi

(ventricularInteraction_flat.Vrv + ventricularInteraction_flat.Vsept) * ventricularInteraction_flat.A * exp((-ventricularInteraction_flat.B) * (ventricularInteraction_flat.tm - ventricularInteraction_flat.CC) ^ 2.0) * ventricularInteraction_flat.Esrv + (1.0 - ventricularInteraction_flat.A * exp((-ventricularInteraction_flat.B) * (ventricularInteraction_flat.tm - ventricularInteraction_flat.CC) ^ 2.0)) * ventricularInteraction_flat.Pi0rv * (-1.0 + exp(ventricularInteraction_flat.lambdarv * (ventricularInteraction_flat.Vrv + ventricularInteraction_flat.Vsept))) + ventricularInteraction_flat.Pperi

(ventricularInteraction_flat.Vsept - ventricularInteraction_flat.V0sept) * ventricularInteraction_flat.A * exp((-ventricularInteraction_flat.B) * (ventricularInteraction_flat.tm - ventricularInteraction_flat.CC) ^ 2.0) * ventricularInteraction_flat.Essept + (1.0 - ventricularInteraction_flat.A * exp((-ventricularInteraction_flat.B) * (ventricularInteraction_flat.tm - ventricularInteraction_flat.CC) ^ 2.0)) * ventricularInteraction_flat.Pi0sept * (-1.0 + exp(ventricularInteraction_flat.lambdas * ventricularInteraction_flat.Vsept))
mitralValve._Goff * mitralValve.Pknee + mitralValve.passableVariable * (if mitralValve.open then 1.0 else mitralValve._Goff) - Lmt.state
tricuspidValve._Goff * tricuspidValve.Pknee + tricuspidValve.passableVariable * (if tricuspidValve.open then 1.0 else tricuspidValve._Goff) - Ltc.state
pulmonaryValve._Goff * pulmonaryValve.Pknee + pulmonaryValve.passableVariable * (if pulmonaryValve.open then 1.0 else pulmonaryValve._Goff) - Lpv.state
aorticValve._Goff * aorticValve.Pknee + aorticValve.passableVariable * (if aorticValve.open then 1.0 else aorticValve._Goff) - Lav.state

smooth(0, if noEvent(aorta.state > aorta.CollapsingPressureVolume) then aorta.excessVolume / aorta.Compliance + aorta.ExternalPressure else aorta.a * log(max(1e-015, aorta.state / aorta.CollapsingPressureVolume)) + aorta.ExternalPressure)

smooth(0, if noEvent(venaCava.state > venaCava.CollapsingPressureVolume) then venaCava.excessVolume / venaCava.Compliance + venaCava.ExternalPressure else venaCava.a * log(max(1e-015, venaCava.state / venaCava.CollapsingPressureVolume)) + venaCava.ExternalPressure)
aorticValve._Goff * aorticValve.Pknee + aorticValve.passableVariable * (if aorticValve.open then 1.0 else aorticValve._Goff) - Lav.state
aorticValve.passableVariable * (if aorticValve.open then 1.0 / aorticValve._Gon else 1.0) + aorticValve.Pknee
tricuspidValve._Goff * tricuspidValve.Pknee + tricuspidValve.passableVariable * (if tricuspidValve.open then 1.0 else tricuspidValve._Goff) - Ltc.state
tricuspidValve.passableVariable * (if tricuspidValve.open then 1.0 / tricuspidValve._Gon else 1.0) + tricuspidValve.Pknee
pulmonaryValve._Goff * pulmonaryValve.Pknee + pulmonaryValve.passableVariable * (if pulmonaryValve.open then 1.0 else pulmonaryValve._Goff) - Lpv.state
pulmonaryValve.passableVariable * (if pulmonaryValve.open then 1.0 / pulmonaryValve._Gon else 1.0) + pulmonaryValve.Pknee

smooth(0, if noEvent(pulmonaryArteries.state > pulmonaryArteries.CollapsingPressureVolume) then pulmonaryArteries.excessVolume / pulmonaryArteries.Compliance + IntraThoracicPressure.k else pulmonaryArteries.a * log(max(1e-015, pulmonaryArteries.state / pulmonaryArteries.CollapsingPressureVolume)) + IntraThoracicPressure.k)

smooth(0, if noEvent(pulmonaryVeins.state > pulmonaryVeins.CollapsingPressureVolume) then pulmonaryVeins.excessVolume / pulmonaryVeins.Compliance + IntraThoracicPressure.k else pulmonaryVeins.a * log(max(1e-015, pulmonaryVeins.state / pulmonaryVeins.CollapsingPressureVolume)) + IntraThoracicPressure.k)
mitralValve._Goff * mitralValve.Pknee + mitralValve.passableVariable * (if mitralValve.open then 1.0 else mitralValve._Goff) - Lmt.state
mitralValve.passableVariable * (if mitralValve.open then 1.0 / mitralValve._Gon else 1.0) + mitralValve.Pknee

(ventricularInteraction_flat.Vrv + ventricularInteraction_flat.Vsept) * ventricularInteraction_flat.A * $cse6 * ventricularInteraction_flat.Esrv + (1.0 - ventricularInteraction_flat.A * $cse6) * ventricularInteraction_flat.Pi0rv * (-1.0 + $cse8) + ventricularInteraction_flat.Pperi

(ventricularInteraction_flat.Vlv - ventricularInteraction_flat.Vsept) * ventricularInteraction_flat.A * $cse6 * ventricularInteraction_flat.Eslv + (1.0 - ventricularInteraction_flat.A * $cse6) * ventricularInteraction_flat.Pi0lv * (-1.0 + $cse7) + ventricularInteraction_flat.Pperi
